    <h1>Self-Assessment Questionnaire: Building Resilience</h1>
    <p>As a follow-up to the ‘Introduction to Building resilience’ session on 20 May and in preparation of the follow-up session on 18 June (under the Avertim’Her brand), you can here reflect on and assess your resilience mindset across key dimensions that are critical in fast-paced, cognitively demanding environments like consulting. The questionnaire is inspired by the BetterUp Lab research.</p>
    <p>To do so, rate yourself on a scale from 1 (Strongly Disagree) to 5 (Strongly Agree) for each statement. Be Honest-this is for your own growth.</p>
    <label for="firstName">Name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" placeholder="What is your name">

